Detectives probing the mystery murder of businesswoman Monica Nyawira Kimani are detaining a Recce squad officer after arresting the officer Thursday evening. Jennings Okoth Orlando alias Odhiambo was arrested in Nairobi and taken to the Muthaiga police station before being interrogated at the Directorate Of Criminal Investigations headquarters. The suspect who is believed to have been with key suspect  Joseph Irungu Jowie at Monica’s apartment on the night she was killed will be detained for 14days after being presented at the Kimabu law courts.  